Log::Funlog::Lang - Language pack for Log::Funlog

Gab
korsani free fr

 ,+---------------------------------- -  -   -    -     -
( | Description
 `+---------------------------------- -  -   -    -     -

Perl module that provide funny sentences for Log::Funlog.

 ,+---------------------------------- -  -   -    -     -
( | Install
 `+---------------------------------- -  -   -    -     -

perl Makefile.PL
make
(make test)
sudo make install

 ,+---------------------------------- -  -   -    -     -
( | Use
 `+---------------------------------- -  -   -    -     -
	
	use Log::Funlog::Lang;
	my @fun=Log::Funlog::Lang->new();
